Let's go.

589
00:30:35,110 --> 00:30:36,030
You are tired.

590
00:30:36,190 --> 00:30:37,270
Your whole family is tired.

591
00:30:37,390 --> 00:30:38,550
Do you really think I'm a monkey?

592
00:30:57,310 --> 00:30:58,750
This is the best stinky tofu

593
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,310
in the universe.

594
00:31:00,310 --> 00:31:01,110
Try it.

595
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:03,110
Try it.

596
00:31:08,670 --> 00:31:09,390
Is it good?

597
00:31:10,630 --> 00:31:11,430
Not bad.

598
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,310
Your clothes are dirty.

599
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:41,670
Your face...

600
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:43,870
I'm not blushing.

601
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,110
I mean

602
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:49,470
your face is dirty too.

603
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,550
Well, I'm full.

604
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:55,750
I bought some food for Wukong.

605
00:31:55,990 --> 00:31:57,070
Let's go back.

606
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:09,830
Cushion foundation.

607
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,110
What is this?

608
00:32:13,870 --> 00:32:14,430
This…

609
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,230
Ling Chao must like it

610
00:32:23,230 --> 00:32:25,030
if you wear this.

611
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,630
Jiang Juanjuan.

612
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:38,550
Coming.

613
00:32:50,190 --> 00:32:51,990
The electric kettle in our room is broken.

614
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:54,950
Can I use yours to boil some water?

615
00:32:56,190 --> 00:32:57,790
You're so polite.

616
00:32:58,390 --> 00:32:59,310
Come in.

617
00:33:03,430 --> 00:33:05,110
Let me help you.

618
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:06,990
I can do it myself.

619
00:33:33,750 --> 00:33:34,750
You're

620
00:33:35,910 --> 00:33:37,350
a little different today.

621
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:41,670
Is it that obvious?

622
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,390
I can feel

623
00:33:47,190 --> 00:33:48,590
that you put some effort into it.

624
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:51,190
Let me explain.

625
00:33:51,190 --> 00:33:51,870
It's not mine.

626
00:33:51,870 --> 00:33:52,550
It's really not mine.

627
00:33:52,550 --> 00:33:53,390
Not mine.

628
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:55,630
Why didn't you dry your hair?

629
00:33:55,870 --> 00:33:56,750
It's easy to catch a cold

630
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:57,750
in this season.

631
00:33:58,670 --> 00:34:00,430
It's okay. I'm inside the room...

632
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,310
Don't move.

633
00:34:27,949 --> 00:34:28,469
Itchy.

634
00:35:07,310 --> 00:35:08,590
Ling Chao.

635
00:35:10,270 --> 00:35:11,870
I must talk to you.

636
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:12,990
What?

637
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:15,470
We have a big competition tomorrow.

638
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:17,750
It's not good to be so tired

639
00:35:18,710 --> 00:35:19,470
the night before the competition.

640
00:35:33,990 --> 00:35:34,710
Go to sleep.

641
00:35:35,870 --> 00:35:36,710
We'll win first place

642
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:38,830
when we wake up.
